  "contentHtml": "<!-- BEGIN COPYRIGHTED TEXT CHUNK --><html><head></head><body><div class=\"chapter\">\n<!--jtb 021201: AG counts this sutta as AN 2.92. As near as I can figure, PTS counts it as II.98. -->\n<p>\"Monks, these two are fools. Which two? The one who takes up a burden that hasn't fallen to him, and the one who doesn't take up a burden that has. These two are fools.\"</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"seeAlso\">\n<p>See also: <a href=\"/tipitaka/an/an02/an02.021.than\">AN 2.21</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n</body></html>",
